      "value": "<p>You can shield others from harm at the cost of your own health. When a creature within your Aura of Protection takes damage, you can use take a Reaction to magically take that damage, instead of that creature taking it. This feature does not transfer any other effects that might accompany the damage, and you can gain Resistance to this damage by expending 5 Hit Points from your Lay on Hands pool.</p>",
